nto their roles. Jorge Losa joined the management roster in 2024.\nRole in Portfolio:—\nMorningstar Medalist Rating\nMorningstar Medalist Ratings/Pillar Scores are assigned based on (1)\nan analyst’s qualitative assessment, either directly or indirectly or (2) The team has a vast universe to cover and thus relies to some extent on sell-side research, but this strategy\nusing algorithmic techniques intended to be similar to those an analyst\nmight assign if he/she had covered the vehicle. Investment vehicles are\nevaluated on three key pillars. Qualitative investment research is pro- (with funds called Cartesio X in Spain and Cartesio Income in Luxembourg) has a patient, value-oriented,\nduced and issued by subsidiaries of Morningstar, Inc. Quantitatively-\ndriven analysis is generated using mental models meant to mirror ana-\nlyst-driven written analysis. and established process that helps narrow the opportunity set. There are two sources of alpha here: asset\nallocation across equity (maximum 40%, since-inception average 20%), bond (including maximum 30% in\n2015 2016 2017 2018 2019 2020 2021 2022 2023 2024 YTD\nInvestment Style\nEquity Style Box\nFixed Income Style Box\nFixed Income Style Box\nTotal Return % (EUR)\n1.89 1.78 3.63 -3.21 4.59 -1.87 5.20 -2.94 10.26 8.58 5.10 Investment\n1.65 1.75 2.50 -4.79 6.71 0.70 3.79 -10.30 6.77 4.95 1.66 Category Average\nWeight% Surveyed 31 May 2025 2.57 2.91 2.19 -1.58 8.35 3.21 2.25 -13.37 7.46 4.47 1.84 Category Index\n50+ Performance Quartile\n25-49 * * * * ( ) * & & & N/A (within Category)\n10-24\n44 50 26 26 75 85 29 4 9 8 N/A Percentile Rank\n0-9\n737 794 877 950 976 968 987 961 970 941 947 # of Inv in Cat.\nYTD Investment as of 30 Jun 2025 | Category: EAA Fund EUR Cautious Allocation as of 8 Jul 2025 | Index: Morningstar EU Cau Tgt Alloc NR EUR as of 8 Jul 2025 | Italics indicate Extended\nPerformance. Extended performance is an estimate based on the performance of the fund's oldest share class, adjusted for fees. Per